        "min": 10,
        "max": 90,
        "value": 70,
        "unit": "%",
        "description": "Ensures uniform coverage and avoids gaps in cleaning; 70% optimal for even fluence distribution on reflective, delicate surfaces like lead crystal. Source: Process optimization in Journal of Laser Applications."
